pdc_discovery.title: Plausible downloads are not showing up

comments.body: Deployed v1.25.3 that includes the period parameter using `12mo` and the values now look correct. But this will only work until we hit the 12 month mark. We should reach out to Plausible to see if there is a way to request `all` as the period.

The `period` parameter supports a [custom date range](https://plausible.io/docs/stats-api#time-periods) that might be what we need:

```
period=custom&date=2021-01-01,2021-01-31
```
